CustomField.description: If the agent was using the Natterbox CTI, this is the amount of time between the call being completed and the agent pressing the 'Done' button on the CTI. If the agent is not making use of the CTI, this field will be left blank.
CustomField.inlineHelpText: If the agent was using the Natterbox CTI, this is the amount of time between the call being completed and the agent pressing the 'Done' button on the CTI. If the agent is not making use of the CTI, this field will be left blank.
CustomField.label: Wrapup Time
